advance payment policy of proprietary research activities at stanford synchrotron radiation lightsource page 1 advance payment policy of proprietary research activities at stanford synchrotron radiation lightsource in accordance with the doe accounting policies proprietary research experiments performed at the stanford synchrotron radiation lightsource shall neither start nor continue without full prepayment or a cash advance of funds ssrl therefore applies the following advance payment protocol high activity users must deposit in advance each year an amount corresponding to their projected usage for private sector research for the entire fiscal year run time new or infrequent users must pay for the scheduled shifts in advance of their experiment after termination of private sector research activities any outstanding balance will be refunded august 1 2009 piero pianetta acting ssrl director
